{"tid":2304391,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【行山/Outdoor撚】日本岩畳之旅","createTime":"2020-11-28T17:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T08:10:00.000Z","uid":226355,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf89743d7337ee8d8d7b257541635347cc666c6","tid":2304391,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"又係我，話說上星期去完岡山玩，今個周未去左關東果邊行下。<br />\n想睇我上星期既相可以去呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2299527/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2299527/page/1</a><br />\n又或者follow 我IG 可以睇到日本唔同地方既風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/___asai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F___asai%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5a1141d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/___asai/</a><br />\n<br />\n一早起身見天氣咁好，即刻check下有邊度好去。<br />\n秋高氣爽，最好就係去行山，今次試下挑戰下高難度去行岩畳。<br />\n搭左兩個半鐘車，終於到達。<br />\n因為關東肺炎爆到七彩，周圍都真係冇乜人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Bkred.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Bkred.png&h=764aafdf&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n往年勁多人要排隊搭既觀光船都唔見人龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H43ShmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH43ShmK.png&h=040371a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今次去既岩畳旁邊仲有一條溪流，加埋紅葉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9za5CqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9za5CqZ.png&h=11715e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然有少少危險，但真係勁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGmXtt4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGmXtt4.png&h=dd9a68fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n影呀影，突然呢兩位係崖邊飲酒野餐既大叔對我部相機好有興趣<br />\n同我吹左成個鐘水，浪費晒中午既好陽光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到再次出發果陣，個天陰晒，又凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wBMmQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wBMmQr.png&h=84e54c71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n除左觀光船，仲有好多其他既水上活動玩<br />\n其實當地氣溫得 10度，D 日本仔身體真係幾壯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEFJo4B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEFJo4B.png&h=82876bc5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69nPjC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69nPjC9.png&h=f95ed51c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後一段山路都係天陰陰咁，愈行愈灰，相都懶得影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59r8Acb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59r8Acb.png&h=5b3ab2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩畳既盡頭連接住一個楓樹林同山屋，<br />\n好多家庭趁周末出黎BBQ同野餐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y71DXrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY71DXrL.png&h=38cd8927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飢寒交迫既我諗住去山屋度食碗面就走，因為真係太凍，<br />\n點知食完出黎，黃昏既陽光出返晒黎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2FEGUH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2FEGUH.png&h=ab17f2ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n雖然時間有D趕，但我決定回頭由楓樹林行返去起點補返D相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOcr6mW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOcr6mW.png&h=cdacad9e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有陽光即刻靚返晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A82r6ne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA82r6ne.png&h=9ef4d13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T81P386.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT81P386.png&h=e9436046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9S38AR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9S38AR.png&h=0250ced5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次就分享住咁多先，紅葉時期我每個周末都會去旅行<br />\n大家想即時睇到日本既風景，記得去我IG 睇 story 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/___asai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F___asai%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5a1141d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/___asai/</a>"},{"pid":"2164b30f01c5ecaae86f20dd83bcc62950a53997","tid":2304391,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf89743d7337ee8d8d7b257541635347cc666c6","tid":2304391,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"又係我，話說上星期去完岡山玩，今個周未去左關東果邊行下。<br />\n想睇我上星期既相可以去呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2299527/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2299527/page/1</a><br />\n又或者follow 我IG 可以睇到日本唔同地方既風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/___asai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F___asai%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5a1141d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/___asai/</a><br />\n<br />\n一早起身見天氣咁好，即刻check下有邊度好去。<br />\n秋高氣爽，最好就係去行山，今次試下挑戰下高難度去行岩畳。<br />\n搭左兩個半鐘車，終於到達。<br />\n因為關東肺炎爆到七彩，周圍都真係冇乜人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Bkred.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Bkred.png&h=764aafdf&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n往年勁多人要排隊搭既觀光船都唔見人龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H43ShmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH43ShmK.png&h=040371a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今次去既岩畳旁邊仲有一條溪流，加埋紅葉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9za5CqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9za5CqZ.png&h=11715e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然有少少危險，但真係勁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGmXtt4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvG